item.description:
Come out  for a night of fun, dancing, laughter,  with bunch of fun peeps for the evening.

Spiral Circus:

We pride ourselves on an ever growing song list, that contains songs from the 60's right up to today.

You want a night of Classic Rock -n- Roll, we can do that.

A night of Pop & Disco to dance the night away, we can do that.

How about a night of Rock / Classic Rock / Pop / Disco and even a little Counrty.

We can definitely do that!

We have you covered, when you come to a Spiral Circus show you will never hear the exact same set list night to night.

You can meet in the lounge before the band starts grab a few tables, have appetizers and drinks. If any one wants to eat  full course dinner come early to grab a few tables, No reservations,  difficult on a Friday night to reserve and I always find its  quicker service in the lounge area, no waiting for those tasty drinks ;-)))

*****THERE WILL NOw BE A HOST FOR THIS EVENT,, THIS IS A GREAT PERFOMING BAND******* AFTER 8 there is a small cover charge think 5.00., parking fills so come early.

Band: Spiral Circus

Time: 9-9:30
